Function Reference/permalink comments rss « WordPress Codex
-----------

Displays the [permalink](/Glossary#Permalink "Glossary") to the post to
which a comment belongs, formatted for [RSS](/Glossary#RSS "Glossary").
Typically used in the RSS comment feed template. This tag must be within
[The Loop](/The_Loop "The Loop"), or a comment loop.

Usage
-----

`  <?php permalink_comments_rss(); ?> `

Example
-------

    <link><?php permalink_comments_rss(); ?></link>

Parameters
----------

This tag has no parameters.

